{"tid":114183,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"【電影音樂台】【六弄咖啡館】《轉車》原：半句再見","createTime":"2017-02-09T14:37:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-22T05:41:29.000Z","uid":41326,"like":39,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ea689f77f9306fe4a6147dab27eb3a8cad9e86f9","tid":114183,"uid":41326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T14:37:52.000Z","msg":"歌：<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RLzfNFMXm6w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRLzfNFMXm6w&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=f3309194\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RLzfNFMXm6w</a><br />\n<br />\n各位連巴連絲大家好，唔知大家有無睇過六弄咖啡館呢套戲<br />\n套戲好似喺香港完全唔紅，但係個人覺得幾好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己覺得比起我的少女時代更加有貼地感<br />\n<br />\n睇完都SAD左好幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知有無人都睇過呢套戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 路過聽下首歌大家傾下計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n----------------<br />\n<br />\n主唱：甲乙丙戊<br />\n填詞：挽歌之聲<br />\n<br />\n若你倦了 就告別了 沒刻寫路標<br />\n苦等的我 在放聲大叫<br />\n從沒有所料 從沒有先兆 <br />\n美麗園林破落難逃蕭條<br />\n<br />\n讓最重要 做個玩笑 烈火不斷燒<br />\n燒光一臉稚氣 吃不消<br />\n狂熱心跳 剩多少 想歸去 無車票<br />\n用最軟聲調喚不回昨宵<br />\n<br />\n不寫你 也不寫我 怎續寫<br />\n登不上你青春尾班列車<br />\n陳夢與那一些 年輪在拉扯<br />\n說的謊撒的野 也阻不了行車<br />\n<br />\n不捨 你再不捨 作傷害者<br />\n傷者 與第三者 要取或捨<br />\n成熟與那一些 情仇在拉扯<br />\n最初不顧陡斜 最終失散荒野 轉車<br />\n<br />\n用上合照 換上獨照 時日在遠漂<br />\n風箏掙脫又返有多少<br />\n無論知曉 未知曉 不心跳 才開竅<br />\n沒結果就算我喚得回昨宵<br />\n<br />\n不寫你 也不寫我 怎續寫<br />\n登不上你青春尾班列車<br />\n陳夢與那一些 年輪在拉扯<br />\n說的謊撒的野 也阻不了行車<br />\n<br />\n不捨 你再不捨 作傷害者<br />\n傷者 與第三者 要取或捨<br />\n成熟與那一些 情仇在拉扯<br />\n最初不顧陡斜 最終失散荒野 轉車<br />\n<br />\n----------------------<br />\n<br />\n原曲：半句再見<br />\n原唱：孫燕姿<br />\n作曲：李偲菘 <br />\n原詞：吳子雲<br />\n電影：六弄咖啡館"},{"pid":"a221f3c970f03e4fc9e8a693b1923e5be2947410","tid":114183,"uid":15309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T14:56:54.000Z","msg":"loop左幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇個mv都覺得sad<br />\n唔敢睇套戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c243d6b73d1f3d8a5fdc14aee360d16f36662362","tid":114183,"uid":33507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T16:00:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6ce4fa971ad4506a0399b38308e2ab9f09ea8fa","tid":114183,"uid":41326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T16:01:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>loop左幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇個mv都覺得sad<br />\n唔敢睇套戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打<br />\n呢套野個男女主角其實真係做得唔錯<br />\n除左口音一個大陸一台灣之外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有機會真係要睇下呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98391ac38f0d897223e38bc2a71c69878231cb9e","tid":114183,"uid":28739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T16:04:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d691af9c718f5792cdc4b3c46b2351d024c6a499","tid":114183,"uid":26878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T16:05:26.000Z","msg":"毒瘤唔睇呢啲戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e99eb812724ab4db8272ad1976b42763a2dfabcb","tid":114183,"uid":41326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T16:09:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n死氣真快手呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hk