uid":34989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T11:57:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ba4a602d0b957aedde5398b86726256bdbb8a25","tid":114183,"uid":33507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T12:01:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1b7a30e47268a552daaebcbb99c06256f7a48f0","tid":114183,"uid":50072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T13:43:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>歌：<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RLzfNFMXm6w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRLzfNFMXm6w&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=f3309194\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RLzfNFMXm6w</a><br />\n<br />\n各位連巴連絲大家好，唔知大家有無睇過六弄咖啡館呢套戲<br />\n套戲好似喺香港完全唔紅，但係個人覺得幾好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己覺得比起我的少女時代更加有貼地感<br />\n<br />\n睇完都SAD左好幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知有無人都睇過呢套戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 路過聽下首歌大家傾下計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n----------------<br />\n<br />\n主唱：甲乙丙戊<br />\n填詞：挽歌之聲<br />\n<br />\n若你倦了 就告別了 沒刻寫路標<br />\n苦等的我 在放聲大叫<br />\n從沒有所料 從沒有先兆 <br />\n美麗園林破落難逃蕭條<br />\n<br />\n讓最重要 做個玩笑 烈火不斷燒<br />\n燒光一臉稚氣 吃不消<br />\n狂熱心跳 剩多少 想歸去 無車票<br />\n用最軟聲調喚不回昨宵<br />\n<br />\n不寫你 也不寫我 怎續寫<br />\n登不上你青春尾班列車<br />\n陳夢與那一些 年輪在拉扯<br />\n說的謊撒的野 也阻不了行車<br />\n<br />\n不捨 你再不捨 作傷害者<br />\n傷者 與第三者 要取或捨<br />\n成熟與那一些 情仇在拉扯<br />\n最初不顧陡斜 最終失散荒野 轉車<br />\n<br />\n用上合照 換上獨照 時日在遠漂<br />\n風箏掙脫又返有多少<br />\n無論知曉 未知曉 不心跳 才開竅<br />\n沒結果就算我喚得回昨宵<br />\n<br />\n不寫你 也不寫我 怎續寫<br />\n登不上你青春尾班列車<br />\n陳夢與那一些 年輪在拉扯<br />\n說的謊撒的野 也阻不了行車<br />\n<br />\n不捨 你再不捨 作傷害者<br />\n傷者 與第三者 要取或捨<br />\n成熟與那一些 情仇在拉扯<br />\n最初不顧陡斜 最終失散荒野 轉車<br />\n<br />\n----------------------<br />\n<br />\n原曲：半句再見<br />\n原唱：孫燕姿<br />\n作曲：李偲菘 <br />\n原詞：吳子雲<br />\n電影：六弄咖啡館</blockquote><br />\n甲乙丙戊絲打把聲好似孫燕芝同謝安琪<br />\n會唔會有自創歌曲聽<br />\n利申：皮以正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67da2c626b253b4cd50e9954f68a6f9ae4da6a33","tid":114183,"uid":33507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T16:35:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec1bdbf76f6a5b921fc1f1fe09f32447199288ba","tid":114183,"uid":33507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T17:20:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d7dcdc0448468b7e89193952fe0805a42a51a4f","tid":114183,"uid":11876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T03:42:04.000Z","msg":"竟然無人屌個女主角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩岩走去睇，個女主角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b064964b82cb7ab0393947601b0becd3a82ea13","tid":114183,"uid":2984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T12:30:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>竟然無人屌個女主角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩岩走去睇，個女主角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇完唔會想屌女主角，現實就係咁殘酷<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"599d171738c5be53bc637f5b0378342300d4bbdd","tid":114183,"uid":33507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T13:47:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f7eb8c3b31687bf390ec4dfca72b7f0263c05b0","tid":114183,"uid":33507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T15:47:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f93be419db6a786319b074f15afa8e43b39de